import React from 'react'
import CardItem from './CardItem'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'


const Home = () => {
  return (
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col className='mt-3'><CardItem/></Col>  
                <Col className='mt-3'><CardItem/></Col>        
                <Col className='mt-3'><CardItem/></Col>        
                <Col className='mt-3'><CardItem/></Col>        
            </Row>
        </Container>
  )
}

export default Home
